804
00:59:39,359 --> 00:59:41,862
Hindi, ayos lang. Hindi na kailangan.
Tatawagan na lang kita ulit.

805
00:59:42,029 --> 00:59:43,447
Bababa na lang ako rito.

806
00:59:44,073 --> 00:59:45,365
Medyo malayo pa rin ito mula rito.

807
00:59:45,449 --> 00:59:48,327
Kakalampas lang ng intersection... In-a!

808
01:00:04,551 --> 01:00:05,761
Nakakadurog ng puso.

809
01:00:10,641 --> 01:00:12,142
Siguro nalulungkot ka nang sobra.

810
01:00:15,521 --> 01:00:17,106
Patuloy kang umaarte nang matapang

811
01:00:19,900 --> 01:00:21,068
